Custom Open Kitchen With Recess Lighting, Upgraded Wine Fridge, Stainless Steel Appliances, Built-In Gas Range on the Large Island and Much Much More. 4 Bedrooms and Laundry Area Upstairs. Digital Keypad Smart Locks, Security System, Ecobee Thermostats, Motion Activated Lights in Bathrooms, Smart Fans and Wood Faux Blinds All Convey.
